# Quezon City University Information

## School Information

**School Name:** Quezon City University
**Address:** 673 Quirino Highway, San Bartolome, Novaliches, Quezon City, Philippines
**Phone:** (02) 8806-3049
**Email:** qcu.edu
**Website:** [Quezon City University Official Website](https://qcu.edu.ph/?utm_source=chatgpt.com)

