# Academic Programs

## College of Computer Studies

* Bachelor of Science in Information Technology
* Bachelor of Science in Computer Science
* Bachelor of Science in Information Systems

## College of Education

* Bachelor of Early Childhood Education

## College of Engineering

* Bachelor of Science in Industrial Engineering
* Bachelor of Science in Electronics Engineering

## College of Business

* Bachelor of Science in Entrepreneurship

## College of Accountancy

* Bachelor of Science in Accountancy

---

# Tuition

Commission on Higher Education and the Universal Access to Quality Tertiary Education Act (RA 10931) allow qualified students of Quezon City University to enjoy **free tuition and waived miscellaneous fees** through the UniFAST program.

